text: “The @EU_Commission president added she would have no concerns about being vaccinated with the @AstraZeneca jab. ‘I would be vaccinated with the #vaccine from AstraZeneca just as safely as with the products from #BioNTech / #Pfizer or #moderna’, [@vonderleyen] said.” #COVID19 https://t.co/5J1kNhQPnf
